'''500米口径球面射电望远镜'''（{{lang-en|'''F'''ive-hundred-meter '''A'''perture '''S'''pherical radio '''T'''elescope}}，简称'''FAST'''）又被称为“'''中国天眼'''”，是[[中国科学院国家天文台|中国科学院国家天文台]]的一座[[射电望远镜|射电望远镜]]，其落成後至今仍是為世界上最大的單孔徑望遠鏡。

FAST主体工程于2011年开工，2016年落成；是目前世界第一大的填充口径（即全口径均有反射面的）射电望远镜<ref name="Brinks">{{cite web
  | last = Brinks
  | first = Elias
  | title = China Opens the Aperture to the Cosmos
  | work = The Conversation
  | publisher = [[US_News_and_World_Report|US News and World Report]]
  | date = 2016-07-11
  | url = https://www.usnews.com/news/best-countries/articles/2016-07-11/china-builds-worlds-largest-radio-telescope
  | accessdate = 2016-08-12
  | archive-date = 2016-08-26
  | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160826032054/http://www.usnews.com/news/best-countries/articles/2016-07-11/china-builds-worlds-largest-radio-telescope
  | dead-url = no
  }}</ref>；若是不局限於球面無線電望遠鏡，則屬於仅次俄罗斯[[RATAN-600|RATAN-600环状射电望远镜]]的，世界第二大的单一口径射电望远镜<ref>{{cite news|url=http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/s/2015-11-24/doc-ifxkxfvn8987505.shtml|title=说说那些奇形怪状的天文望远镜:FAST是最大的吗|date=2015-11-24|accessdate=2017-10-10|work=科普中国|archive-date=2017-10-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171011021614/http://tech.sina.com.cn/d/s/2015-11-24/doc-ifxkxfvn8987505.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

==历史==
[[File:FAST_under_construction,_took_from_rim..jpg|thumb]]

1994年，[[国家天文台|国家天文台]]提出建造FAST项目的设想并开展预研工作。1994年4月，预研究及贵州选址工作启动<ref name="cctv">{{cite web
| url = http://v.qq.com/page/l/u/r/l0020an8uur.html
| title = 观天巨眼FAST望远镜诞生记
| accessdate = 2016-07-03
| archive-date = 2016-07-17
| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160717180355/http://v.qq.com/page/l/u/r/l0020an8uur.html
| dead-url = no
}}</ref>。

以[[哈尔滨工业大学|哈尔滨工业大学]]空间结构研究中心[[沈世钊|沈世钊]]院士、范峰教授、钱宏亮教授为首的研究团队，自2003年起全程参与FAST项目结构系统的预研、可行性研究和初步设计。

在2007年7月[[中華人民共和國國家發展和改革委員會|國家發展及改革委員會]]批准此一專案{{r|IAU 2007|Normile}}<ref name="cctv"></ref>，哈工大作为第一合作单位，负责反射面结构系统的初步设计。

經過考察，望远镜的建设定点定在[[贵州省|贵州省]][[平塘县|平塘县]][[克度镇|克度镇]][[大窝凼洼地|大窝凼洼地]]，利用[[喀斯特|喀斯特]]洼地的地势而建，村民随即搬迁{{r|Xinhua complete}}；为了避开电磁波干扰，居住在望遠鏡半徑5公里內的9,110位居民亦被搬遷<ref name="Xinhua complete">{{Cite news |title=Xinhua Insight: Installation complete on world's largest radio telescope |url=http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/03/c_135485389.htm |date=2016-07-03 |journal=[[Xinhua|Xinhua]] |accessdate=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2017-11-16 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171116054335/http://news.xinhuanet.com/english/2016-07/03/c_135485389.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite news |title=China Telescope to Displace 9,000 Villagers in Hunt for Extraterrestrials |first=Edward |last=Wong |journal=New York Times |date=2016-02-17 |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/18/world/asia/china-fast-telescope-guizhou-relocation.html |quote=The report said officials were moving 2,029 families, a total of 9,110 people, who live within about three miles of the telescope in the area of Pingtang and Luodian Counties in the southwestern province of Guizhou. Depopulating the area will create "a sound electromagnetic wave environment" for the telescope, Xinhua said. |accessdate=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2019-12-18 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20191218182513/https://www.nytimes.com/2016/02/18/world/asia/china-fast-telescope-guizhou-relocation.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>。中國政府為當地居民的搬遷投入了約2.69億美元的扶貧資金和銀行貸款，而望遠鏡本身的建設費用僅為1.8億美元<ref>{{cite news |title=The Quest For Life Beyond Earth: The World's Largest Radio Telescope Just Went Online |first1=Cecille |last1=De Jesus |editor-first=Patrick |editor-last=Caughill |date=2016-09-26 |journal=Futurism |url=https://futurism.com/the-quest-for-life-beyond-earth-the-worlds-largest-radio-telescope-just-went-online/ |accessdate=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2019-04-12 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190412034819/https://futurism.com/the-quest-for-life-beyond-earth-the-worlds-largest-radio-telescope-just-went-online |dead-url=no }}</ref>。在2008年12月26日，在施工現場舉行了奠基儀式<ref>{{cite web |url=http://gzrb.gog.com.cn/system/2008/12/27/010441147.shtml |title=<span lang="zh-Hans">中国科学院·贵州省共建国家重大科技基础设施500米口径球面射电望远镜（ＦＡＳＴ）项目奠基</span> |language=zh |publisher=Guizhou Daily |date=2008-12-27 |accessdate=2008-12-28 |dead-url=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20090112030246/http://gzrb.gog.com.cn/system/2008/12/27/010441147.shtml |archivedate=2009-01-12 }}</ref>。2011年3月25日，FAST工程正式开工建设<ref name="cctv"></ref>{{r|gm}}<ref name=arxiv>{{cite journal |arxiv=1105.3794 |title=The Five-Hundred-Meter Aperture Spherical Radio Telescope (FAST) Project |author1=Rendong Nan |author2=Di Li |author3=Chengjin Jin |author4=Qiming Wang |author5=Lichun Zhu |author6=Wenbai Zhu |author7=Haiyan Zhang |author8=Youling Yue |author9=Lei Qian |journal=International Journal of Modern Physics D |volume=20 |issue=6 |pages=989–1024 |date=2011-05-20 |doi=10.1142/S0218271811019335|bibcode = 2011IJMPD..20..989N }}</ref>。2012年12月31日，台址开挖主体工程竣工<ref name="cctv"></ref>。2013年12月31日，FAST完成钢结构主动反射面环形支撑圈梁的制造与安装。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.guancha.cn/Science/2014_01_02_196905.shtml|title=中国在建世界最大射电望远镜主体在贵州合龙|publisher=[[观察者网|观察者]]|date=2013-12-31|accessdate=2014-01-02|archive-date=2014-01-05|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140105170849/http://www.guancha.cn/Science/2014_01_02_196905.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年11月30日，馈源支撑塔建成<ref name="cctv"></ref>。2015年2月4日，大跨度索网安装工程完成<ref name="cctv"></ref>。2015年8月2日，第一块反射面单元成功吊装<ref name="cctv"></ref>。2015年11月21日，馈源舱成功起舱进入联调阶段<ref name="cctv"></ref>。2016年7月3日上午，最後一個面板安裝完成{{r|Xinhua complete|arxiv}}<ref>{{cite news |title=China completes installation of world's largest telescope |date=2016-07-03 |journal=The BRICS Post |url=http://thebricspost.com/china-completes-installation-of-worlds-largest-telescope/ |accessdate=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190419162257/http://www.thebricspost.com/china-completes-installation-of-worlds-largest-telescope/ |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref name="CNN 2015">{{cite news |last=McKirdy |first=Euan |url=http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/11/tech/china-fast-telescope/index.html |title=China looks to the stars with creation of world's largest radio telescope |work=CNN News |date=2015-10-12 |accessdate=2015-10-19 |archive-date=2015-10-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20151019000707/http://www.cnn.com/2015/10/11/tech/china-fast-telescope/index.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>，FAST望远镜主体工程完成<ref name="cctv"></ref><ref>{{cite news | url = http://tech.gmw.cn/2016-07/03/content_20811313.htm | title = “观天巨眼”FAST望远镜反射面单元吊装完成 | publisher = [[光明网_(中国)|光明网]] | accessdate = 2016-07-03 | archive-date = 2016-07-04 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160704133745/http://tech.gmw.cn/2016-07/03/content_20811313.htm | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web | url = http://news.cyol.com/content/2016-07/03/content_12999885.htm | title = 世界第一！观天巨眼FAST射电望远镜主体工程完成 | accessdate = 2016-07-06 | date = 2016-07-03 | publisher = 中青在线 | language = zh-Hans | deadurl = yes | archiveurl = https://web.archive.org/web/20160709195039/http://news.cyol.com/content/2016-07/03/content_12999885.htm | archivedate = 2016-07-09 }}</ref>。

2016年9月25日，FAST望远镜正式[[開光|開光]]，開始測試和調適設備<ref name="Morelle BBC">{{cite news |last=Morelle |first=Rebecca |url=https://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-37453933 |title=China's colossal radio telescope begins testing |work=BBC News |date=2016-09-25 |accessdate=2016-09-25 |archive-date=2016-09-25 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160925140311/http://www.bbc.com/news/science-environment-37453933 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。第一次觀測是在主反射器沒有活動的情況，以它固定的形狀配置下進行，並藉由地球的自轉掃描天空{{r|Normile}}。因為較長的波長對反射器形狀誤差的寬容度較大，隨後的早期科學研究將在較低的頻率下進行<ref>{{Cite conference |title=FAST low frequency pulsar survey |first1=Youling |last1=Yue |first2=Di |last2=Li |first3=Rendong |last3=Nan |arxiv=1211.0748 |conference=Neutron Stars and Pulsars: Challenges and Opportunities after 80 years |conference-url=http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/ |date=20–31 August 2012 |doi=10.1017/S174392131300001X |access-date=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2017-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530173653/http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，以使主動表面達到其設計精度<ref>{{cite conference |title=The Five-hundred-meter Aperture Spherical Radio Telescope Project and its Early Science Opportunities |first1=Di |last1=Li |first2=Rendong |last2=Nan |first3=Zhichen |last3=Pan |arxiv=1210.5785 |conference=Neutron Stars and Pulsars: Challenges and Opportunities after 80 years |conference-url=http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/ |date=20–31 August 2012 |doi=10.1017/S1743921312024015 |access-date=2020-01-05 |archive-date=2017-05-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170530173653/http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/ |dead-url=no }} Video available at http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/video/DiLi/ {{Wayback|url=http://www.pulsarastronomy.net/IAUS291/video/DiLi/ |date=20180824173206 }}</ref>。校準各種儀器需要三年的時間，之後就會全面投入運行{{r|Morelle BBC}}，中國進入觀天時代。終極目標在尋找宇宙規律（Looking for the law of the universe）。2017年底，預計首批觀測數據公佈<ref>{{cite news|url=http://news.tvb.com/local/59c78cafe60383de42cb4b13/|title=「超級天眼」模型首於港展出 原型可收宇宙無線電|agency=無綫新聞|date=2017-09-24|language=zh-yue|accessdate=2017-09-25|archive-date=2017-09-25|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170925132115/http://news.tvb.com/local/59c78cafe60383de42cb4b13/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

2017年10月10日，中国科学院宣布FAST首次新发现两颗[[脉冲星|脉冲星]]，其中一颗编号J1859-0131(又名FP1-FAST pulsar #1)，自转周期为1.83秒，据估算距离地球1.6万光年；一颗编号J1931-01(又名FP2，随后被证实该脉冲星已于2007年被美国[[格林班克望远镜|GBT望远镜]]350 MHz 漂移巡天项目所发现<ref>{{Cite web|url=http://crafts.bao.ac.cn/pulsar/fast_all_pulsar_list/|title=List of All Confirmed Pulsar Candidates – CRAFTS|accessdate=2017-11-01|work=crafts.bao.ac.cn|language=en-US|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171107032634/http://crafts.bao.ac.cn/pulsar/fast_all_pulsar_list/|archive-date=2017-11-07|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=http://astro.phys.wvu.edu/GBTdrift350/|title=GBT 350-MHz Drift Scan Pulsar Survey|accessdate=2017-11-01|work=astro.phys.wvu.edu|archive-date=2017-12-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171211023711/http://astro.phys.wvu.edu/GBTdrift350/|dead-url=no}}</ref>)，自转周期0.59秒，据估算距离地球约4100光年。这两颗脉冲星分别由FAST于2017年8月22日、25日在南天银道面通过漂移扫描发现。<ref>{{Cite news|url=http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2017/10-10/8348905.shtml|title=FAST望远镜首次新发现脉冲星 6颗通过国际认证|author=张素|date=2017-10-10|work=中国新闻网|accessdate=2017-10-10|archive-date=2017-10-10|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171010040306/http://www.chinanews.com/gn/2017/10-10/8348905.shtml|dead-url=no}}</ref>

2018年，“中国天眼”安装并调试了专门用于地外文明搜索的后端设备。这个功能有点像筛子的后端设备，主要就是从“中国天眼”浩如烟海的电磁信号中，筛选出有用的窄带候选信号，而把天体和人工信号排除掉。美国加州大学伯克利分校地外文明研究团队基于几十年的地外文明搜索经验，携手中国科学院国家天文台，为“中国天眼”量身开发了这套专门设备。北京师范大学天文系宇宙学与地外文明研究团组张同杰教授预计2020年9月后可以投入新观测，启动针对地外文明的搜索。<ref>{{cite news |title=“中国天眼”预计9月可启动地外文明搜索！ |url=http://www.xhby.net/index/202006/t20200601_6668120.shtml |agency=央视新闻 |publisher=新华报业网 |date=2020/06/01 08:44 |accessdate=2020-06-01 |archive-date=2021-03-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210306174423/http://www.xhby.net/index/202006/t20200601_6668120.shtml }}</ref>

建成后超越[[波多黎各|波多黎各]]的[[阿雷西博天文台|阿雷西博天文台]]，成为世界上最大的單面口徑球面射电望远镜<ref>{{cite news | title = China starts building world's biggest radio telescope | url = https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg21028165.300-china-starts-building-worlds-biggest-radio-telescope | accessdate = 2016-07-03 | publisher = New Scientist | date = 2009-02-02 | archive-date = 2016-07-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20160709180706/https://www.newscientist.com/article/mg21028165.300-china-starts-building-worlds-biggest-radio-telescope | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

该项目最初的預算是人民幣7億元{{r|Nan 2009|p=49|}}<ref name="gm">{{cite web |url=http://www.gizmag.com/five-hundred-meter-aperture-spherical-radio-telescope/18930/ |title=China building world's biggest radio telescope |first=Darren |last=Quick |date=2011-06-16 |accessdate=2012-08-13 |work=gizmag |archive-date=2012-11-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121119193012/http://www.gizmag.com/five-hundred-meter-aperture-spherical-radio-telescope/18930/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>，最終的造價是人民幣12億元（1.8億美元）{{r|Xinhua complete|wanted}}。主鏡促動器也產生無線電干擾，由於沒有現成的防護罩，所以需要自主研製防護罩以抑制主鏡像促動器的[[電磁干擾|電磁干擾]]（radio-frequency interference，RFI）{{r|Normile}}。2015年，主鏡促動器經過重新設計後安裝在FAST，干擾問題已不再發生。<ref>{{Cite web |title=ShieldSquare Captcha |url=https://validate.perfdrive.com/?ssa=63d6374d-0a2e-4113-95b3-5466b39818de&ssb=80821298599&ssc=https%3A%2F%2Fiopscience.iop.org%2Farticle%2F10.1088%2F1674-4527%2F18%2F4%2F48%2Fmeta&ssi=086f0c5e-8427-492e-a6bc-840d1365c9d0&ssk=support@shieldsquare.com&ssm=45182951900263946107668605985799&ssn=57dc5c00d84c84904dcfb00f88dd2edc97bf23b743ed-4cf9-43ef-825865&sso=b9ff8a6c-9bccc613b97547b74c4f3eddacc0f19836d1ea548f5cddc0&ssp=49836715711655078772165508651750178&ssq=48967332404053996554424040212009201727392&ssr=MjA4LjgwLjE1My4yNA==&sst=ZoteroTranslationServer/WMF%20(mailto:noc@wikimedia.org)&ssv=&ssw=&ssx=W10= |website=validate.perfdrive.com |doi=10.1088/1674-4527/18/4/48/meta |access-date=2022-06-12}}</ref>

2018年，FAST安装并调试专门用于地外文明搜索的筛选的窄带候选信号后端设备，该设备由[[加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校|加利福尼亞大學柏克萊分校]]的地外文明研究团队開發；2020年中設備升級，同年9月后投入新观测<ref>{{cite news |author1=何星辉 |title=“中国天眼”搜寻地外文明，天文学家首次透露计划 |url=http://stdaily.com/index/kejixinwen/2020-05/31/content_950201.shtml |accessdate=2020-08-20 |agency=科技日报 |date=2020-05-31 |archive-date=2020-11-05 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20201105075228/http://stdaily.com/index/kejixinwen/2020-05/31/content_950201.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

